vent/clientY","fixable":true,"line":32,"column":24},{"explanation":"Can't resolve https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/screenX","id":"link8","href":"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/screenX","suggestion":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/screenX","fixable":true,"line":33,"column":24},{"explanation":"Can't resolve https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/screenY","id":"link9","href":"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/screenY","suggestion":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/screenY","fixable":true,"line":34,"column":24},{"explanation":"Can't resolve https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/pageX","id":"link10","href":"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/pageX","suggestion":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/pageX","fixable":true,"line":35,"column":22},{"explanation":"Can't resolve https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/pageY","id":"link11","href":"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/pageY","suggestion":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/pageY","fixable":true,"line":36,"column":22},{"explanation":"Can't resolve https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/offsetX","id":"link12","href":"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/offsetX","suggestion":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/offsetX","fixable":true,"line":37,"column":24},{"explanation":"Can't resolve https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/offsetY","id":"link13","href":"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/offsetY","suggestion":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/offsetY","fixable":true,"line":38,"column":24}]},"title":"鼠标事件","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Learn/Framework/Event/MouseEvent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<h1 id=\"兼容性\">兼容性</h1>\n<ul>\n  <li>PC ≥ 5.18</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"使用\">使用</h1>\n<p>在 PC 端小程序中，可以监听如下鼠标事件：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><code>mousedown</code></li>\n  <li><code>mousemove</code></li>\n  <li><code>mouseup</code></li>\n  <li><code>mouseover</code></li>\n  <li><code>mouseenter</code></li>\n  <li><code>mouseout</code></li>\n  <li><code>mouseleave</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>除了基础的事件对象的属性以外，还会有如下属性：</p>\n<div class=\"table-scroll\"><table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>属性</th>\n      <th>类型</th>\n      <th>说明</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>ctrlKey</td>\n      <td>boolean</td>\n      <td>同 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/ctrlKey\" data-flaw=\"link1\">MouseEvent.ctrlKey</a> 一致</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>shiftKey</td>\n      <td>boolean</td>\n      <td>同 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/shiftKey\" data-flaw=\"link2\">MouseEvent.shiftKey</a> 一致</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>altKey</td>\n      <td>boolean</td>\n      <td>同 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/altKey\" data-flaw=\"link3\">MouseEvent.altKey</a> 一致</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>metaKey</td>\n      <td>boolean</td>\n      <td>同 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/metaKey\" data-flaw=\"link4\">MouseEvent.metaKey</a> 一致</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>button</td>\n      <td>number</td>\n      <td>同 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/button\" data-flaw=\"link5\">MouseEvent.button</a> 一致</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>relatedTarget</td>\n      <td>EventTarget</td>\n      <td>同 <code>target</code> 属性一致，如果不存在则为 null</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>clientX</td>\n      <td>number</td>\n      <td>同 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/clientX\" data-flaw=\"link6\">MouseEvent.clientX</a> 一致</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>clientY</td>\n      <td>number</td>\n      <td>同 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/clientY\" data-flaw=\"link7\">MouseEvent.clientY</a> 一致</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>screenX</td>\n      <td>number</td>\n      <td>同 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/screenX\" data-flaw=\"link8\">MouseEvent.screenX</a> 一致</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>screenY</td>\n      <td>number</td>\n      <td>同 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/screenY\" data-flaw=\"link9\">MouseEvent.screenY</a> 一致</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>pageX</td>\n      <td>number</td>\n      <td>同 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/pageX\" data-flaw=\"link10\">MouseEvent.pageX</a> 一致</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>pageY</td>\n      <td>number</td>\n      <td>同 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/pageY\" data-flaw=\"link11\">MouseEvent.pageY</a> 一致</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>offsetX</td>\n      <td>number</td>\n      <td>同 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/offsetX\" data-flaw=\"link12\">MouseEvent.offsetX</a> 一致</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>offsetY</td>\n      <td>number</td>\n      <td>同 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/offsetY\" data-flaw=\"link13\">MouseEvent.offsetY</a> 一致</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table></div>\n<p>当 <code>target</code> 为 <code>canvas</code> 组件的时候，还会存在 <code>x</code>/<code>y</code> 属性。</p>\n<div class=\"table-scroll\"><table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>属性</th>\n      <th>类型</th>\n      <th>说明</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>x</td>\n      <td>number</td>\n      <td>距离 <code>canvas</code> 组件左上角的横向距离</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>y</td>\n      <td>number</td>\n      <td>距离 <code>canvas</code> 组件左上角的纵向距离</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table></div>\n<h1 id=\"tips\">Tips</h1>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    当监听了鼠标事件之后，并不会阻止触摸事件的触发。\n    如果应用程序需要同时运行在移动端和 PC 端，那么需要手动处理两个事件重复触发的情况。\n  </li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"在 PC 端小程序中，可以监听如下鼠标事件：","popularity":0,"modified":null,"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/learn/framework/event/mouseevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/learn/framework/event/mouseevent/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/null","filename":"index.md"},"short_title":"鼠标事件","parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Learn/Framework/Event","title":"事件"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Learn/Framework/Event/MouseEvent","title":"鼠标事件"}],"pageTitle":"鼠标事件 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}